message.content:
A white-walled kitchen and dining area with parquet flooring. Along one wall, there is a tall, black, floor-to-ceiling cabinet and adjacent black upper cabinets. Beneath these cabinets is a beige marble-style countertop. Near the left end of that counter sits a stack of white plates, a jar of strawberry jam, a box of strawberry Jell-O, and a container of Alpen Salt. Next to these is a box labeled “Rice Bubbles” and another box labeled “Chucky” cereal. An orange mug rests on the counter close to a small pot on the stovetop in the corner. Above this corner is a wooden, circular range hood. To the left of the stovetop is a small metal sink directly under a wooden-framed window.

To the right of the cabinets, a white refrigerator stands against the same wall. Nearby, the room opens into a dining area. Centered there is a rectangular wooden table surrounded by four white-cushioned chairs. On the table is a white fruit bowl with several oranges, a large plastic water bottle, a clear pitcher, a single wine glass, and a small rectangular box set off to one side. A white door with a silver handle is visible on the wall beyond the table, and an overhead ceiling light hangs above the dining space.
